#: C/system-admin-guide.xml:100(para)
msgid "Implementation of MIME types in MATE follows the <ulink url=\"http://www.freedesktop.org/Standards/shared-mime-info-spec\">XDG shared mime info specification</ulink>. This specification provides the following advantages:"
